portfolio website using mainly css and sass 

browser doesnt read scss file so we use node-sass as regular compiler to css files
font aswsome.com for fonts

header has 2 parts menu(menu lines) and nav bar (having menu branding and menu-nav )

menu-branding holds the image (not using inline tag)
portrait class is used to insert image 

menu-nav shows menu options
inside menu-nav , li tags are used for showing menu-options 


FOR HEADINGS H1,H2
lg-heaading and sm-heading class is used.

sm-heading = (main.scss file) lighten fn is used to lighten the given
             color as parameter and 2nd parameter is amount to lighten 
             this whole fn is wrapped in (rgba fn) to fade it to bg.
              

 containing 3 btn lines 